    "summary": "The transcript follows a conversation regarding the history of the US Civil Rights Movement. The user moves from asking for a general summary to posing more critical/revisionist questions about whether nonviolence was a \"cleaner narrative\" or a distraction from systemic issues. The assistant responds by acknowledging these academic critiques and explaining the complexities of the movement's strategic debates.",
